::Aerotaur::
       He looked down at Trinity and smiled.  "I couldn't let you help 
because we had to ask the Maximals for help.  They might've thought you were 
an enemy and hurt you. And I couldn't have let that happen.  I know you're a 
fierce Predacon warrior but you still couldn't have faced down the dozen or 
so Maximal warriors that came to our aid."

--part1_b2.6714fc6.299acb70_boundary
